packageYml.name: package.yml
packageYml.content:
matches:
 #GD&T symbols
  # place deg symbol
  - trigger: ":deg"
    replace: "°"
    
    #place diameter symbol
  - trigger: ":dia"
    replace: "Ø"
    
    #place flatness symbol
  - trigger: ":flat"
    replace: "▱"
    
    #place parallelism symbol
  - trigger: ":para"
    replace: "//"
    
    #place concentricity symbol
  - trigger: ":conc"
    replace: "⌾"
    
    #place counterbore symbol
  - trigger: ":cbore"
    replace: "⌴"
    
    #place countersink symbol
  - trigger: ":csink"
    replace: "⌵"
    
    #spotty results with cylindricity
    #place cylindricity symbol
  - trigger: ":cyl"
    replace: "⌭"
    
    #place true position symbol
  - trigger: ":true"
    replace: "⌖"
